nodes.text: A Yinchorri starfighter was a starfighter used by the Yinchorri during their expansion in 33 BBY. Such fighters required one pilot and were armed with a heavy blaster cannon and a medium blaster cannon. These vessels also had two sublight accelerators.
They were not actually built by or for the Yinchorri, but stolen from the Golden Nyss Shipyards.
